trial rocks\ndue to the half life of the radiogenic system. Additionally, such a large and\nlate fractionation in the Sm/Nd ratio would accordingly induce non-observed\nanomalies in the $^{143}$Nd/$^{144}$Nd ratio. Considering our results, the\nGrand Tack model with a late Moon-forming impact cannot be easily reconciled\nwith the Nd isotopic Earth contents.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Mar 2021 18:13:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 9 Mar 2021 13:14:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-14"}
