f deep learning in CCT images would result\nin a huge computational cost) evidence the applicability of our proposal in a\nreal-world environment.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Mar 2021 11:30:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 26 Sep 2022 17:06:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-27"}
